{"tid":838112,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"THE世界大學排名 城大「國際視野」全球第一","createTime":"2018-09-27T01:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T00:06:20.000Z","uid":71543,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"83570f6dd88ff328f51203fc0904ba07bb980bdb","tid":838112,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:16:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吾城<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  WOOOOO 連城一線！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】《泰晤士高等教育》（THE）公布2019年世界大學排名，英國牛津大學繼續蟬聯首位，次位是劍橋大學。榜內本港6所大學中，除科大排名下跌外，其餘皆上升或不變，當中排名最高的香港大學升4名，排36位；<span style=\"color: red;\">城大雖排110位，但其「國際視野」評分為全球第一。內地清華大學擊敗新加坡國立大學成為亞洲第一，位列世界第22。</span><br />\n<br />\n清華排22 亞洲最佳<br />\n<br />\n有關排名計算方法根據「學與教環境」（30%）、「研究量、收入和聲譽」（30%）、「研究影響」（30%）、「國際視野」（7.5%）和「知識轉移收入」（2.5%）。<br />\n<br />\n港大升4位 香港之首<br />\n<br />\n最新排名首兩位與去年一樣，加州理工學院則由第3位跌至第5。<span style=\"color: red;\">本港大學方面，港大排名繼續最高（見表），科大（46）和中大（55）皆在百名內，其中科大排名跌兩位。</span>科大表示排名升跌受不同因素影響，會視之為參考，了解自己及其他大學表現，掌握需要完善之處。<br />\n<br />\n城大和理大排百名外，城大雖位列110，但在「國際員工和學生比例」、「國際合著」表現名列前茅，「國際視野」被評全球第一。翻查資料，城大2017/18學年總學生人數約1.4萬，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其中1545人來自內地</span></strong></span>，695人來自亞洲及其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n城大理大排百名外<br />\n<br />\n城大表示，配合大學發展策略，城大積極延攬全球優秀學者、推動國際研究合作及學生交流。浸大則維持去年排名（401至500）。<br />\n<br />\n內地方面，清華大學超越新加坡國立大學成為亞洲第一，是自2011年按該計分機制後首次有中國院校獲此排名；北京大學則下降4位，跌至第31。"},{"pid":"112fe5194e6f3b3520f838e186c4828b994e1d28","tid":838112,"uid":175598,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afd3cbfca68f11cea0862379ca38a7a974330108","tid":838112,"uid":71543,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"唔記得post埋圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180927/s00050/e754edc6f1ccffe91b78957138c179dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180927%2Fs00050%2Fe754edc6f1ccffe91b78957138c179dd.jpg&h=e350bc4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a7ac4253e5cf20190adbec5e08409eaf0f55384","tid":838112,"uid":93395,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">pound of 吾城<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"6ea5bc41edbcdf26577f3be5fb5c6bc77f82e9ac","tid":838112,"uid":210825,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:34:39.000Z","msg":"吾城又贏 收盡non local<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93482792c08f4620c00f69b634bcb7179daa1b43","tid":838112,"uid":29270,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"當一堆人想讀大學讀唔到既時候<br />\n<br />\n收咁撚多大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd1b25718e2e7a741154f538d605506516b6682","tid":838112,"uid":175598,"like":24,"dislike":5,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ab047fdd5c74c24b3d78c7f19092d8cb6b47168","tid":838112,"uid":4917,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"又搞港獨，支那生當「國際」"},{"pid":"3367fc4c3696ed10fdc61f1c37d4340b913dc225","tid":838112,"uid":166486,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4ab047fdd5c74c24b3d78c7f19092d8cb6b47168","tid":838112,"uid":4917,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"又搞港獨，支那生當「國際」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"Sir yes"},{"pid":"2653b7716adf2ce4e33fc519f3e9310722e730d0","tid":838112,"uid":39021,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"cite